# Guild Warp — Place a destination row at the correct Y position
# Macro args: row (0-5), name, x, y, z, uuid0, uuid1, uuid2, uuid3, warp_free
# Anchored to background entity

# Row Y offsets from background center (6 rows, 0.12 apart):
# 0: +0.30, 1: +0.18, 2: +0.06, 3: -0.06, 4: -0.18, 5: -0.30

# Spawn text_display with destination info
